130
00:08:02,637 --> 00:08:05,521
Jack's efforts or yours?

131
00:08:07,474 --> 00:08:10,860
I'm vomiting my stomach lining.

132
00:08:12,813 --> 00:08:17,183
On a good day, I sleep

133
00:08:17,185 --> 00:08:20,770
fifteen to eighteen hours.

134
00:08:20,772 --> 00:08:22,972
On a bad day, I don't sleep.

135
00:08:22,974 --> 00:08:26,075
My best-case
scenario

136
00:08:26,077 --> 00:08:30,129
is prolonged pain management.

137
00:08:30,131 --> 00:08:32,498
Jack will help you manage.

138
00:08:34,601 --> 00:08:38,554
He loves you, Bella.

139
00:08:38,556 --> 00:08:42,041
When you are gone, he will feel
your silence like a draft.

140
00:08:42,043 --> 00:08:44,260
My silence

141
